      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEA BREEZY (3) steps out for the first time at this course. Comes here a last start placegetter at Shepparton in a Grade 5 (22.72). Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Can measure up this time. LIKE A BLAZE (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (22.93) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at Shepparton. One of the main contenders. THERMAL SPARK (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at Shepparton over 390m behind Rolling Express (23.14) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Cannot be taken lightly. REDEEMER BELLE (4) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - should feature again.",
